msgid ""
"### 6. How to solve the problem of \"Failed to infer device type\" or "
"\"libatb.so: cannot open shared object file\"?"
msgstr ""
"### 6. 如何解决“Failed to infer device type”或“libatb.so: cannot open shared "
"object file”的问题？"

msgid ""
"1. try `source /usr/local/Ascend/nnal/atb/set_env.sh` to enable NNAL package.\n"
"2. try `source /usr/local/Ascend/ascend-toolkit/set_env.sh` to enable CANN package.\n"
"3. try `npu-smi info` to check whether the NPU is working."
msgstr ""
"1. 尝试执行 `source /usr/local/Ascend/nnal/atb/set_env.sh` 以启用 NNAL 包。\n"
"2. 尝试执行 `source /usr/local/Ascend/ascend-toolkit/set_env.sh` 以启用 CANN 包。\n"
"3. 尝试执行 `npu-smi info` 检查 NPU 是否正常工作。"

